01:01:18,347 --> 01:01:21,384
- What are you talking about ?
- Ah, stop, stop, stop !

679
01:01:21,427 --> 01:01:25,181
Oh, no, George ! No !

680
01:01:25,227 --> 01:01:27,502
- Shut up, stop it !
- George...

681
01:01:27,547 --> 01:01:30,778
Stop it, if you don't want
me to throw a scandal, tonight !

682
01:01:30,827 --> 01:01:33,864
- Don't you dare
saying a single word ! - You're wrong if...

683
01:01:33,907 --> 01:01:37,695
Stop it !
Don't make me lose control !

684
01:01:37,747 --> 01:01:41,422
I don't want to drive you crazy,
but you have to listen.

685
01:01:41,467 --> 01:01:43,935
STOP !

686
01:01:45,987 --> 01:01:49,059
- Stop !
- George...

687
01:01:56,947 --> 01:02:00,986
I had to feel it, see it,
this job! And I'm terrified !

688
01:02:01,027 --> 01:02:04,463
I know, it's an horrendous
condemnation !

689
01:02:04,507 --> 01:02:07,704
Come on, Irene, ease up a bit
and do not exaggerate.

690
01:02:07,747 --> 01:02:13,299
Belive me, Andrea, I'm not exaggerating.
I saw very well what's it all about.

691
01:02:14,267 --> 01:02:16,827
And to think they want to raise work
to a godlike status !

692
01:02:16,867 --> 01:02:20,985
Don't you suspect you're being
a victim of your first impressions ?

693
01:02:21,027 --> 01:02:25,305
What did you see about work ?
How's the true work life ?

694
01:02:25,347 --> 01:02:27,577
You saw
the slavery of work,...

695
01:02:27,627 --> 01:02:30,619
..but when we'll have
a full working humanity...

696
01:02:30,667 --> 01:02:34,262
The one you dream about
is a monstrous humanity !

697
01:02:34,307 --> 01:02:37,060
I saw them !
They're just slaves in chains !

698
01:02:37,107 --> 01:02:39,223
How could you think
they would be happier ?

699
01:02:39,267 --> 01:02:44,944
At least they would be less unhappy
and there would be more justice.

700
01:02:44,987 --> 01:02:48,821
And nobody will die from fatigue anymore...

701
01:02:48,867 --> 01:02:52,985
..while others are sitting still
watching him.

702
01:02:53,027 --> 01:02:57,100
It might even be true,
but if everybody would understand...

703
01:02:57,147 --> 01:03:01,982
..that work is not just a duty,
but a condemnation...

704
01:03:02,027 --> 01:03:06,976
''You'll earn your bread
by the sweat of your forehead.''

705
01:03:07,027 --> 01:03:11,305
Then, probably,
we'll feel closer,...

706
01:03:11,347 --> 01:03:14,783
..equal, humiliated
in the same way,...

707
01:03:14,827 --> 01:03:17,660
..and we'll search for salvation together.

708
01:03:17,707 --> 01:03:20,858
But I thank you, Andrea,
after all, it was you that brought me to this point.

709
01:03:20,907 --> 01:03:26,664
I know I've been wrong all my life
and there's so little time...

710
01:03:26,707 --> 01:03:29,699
Oh, Michel !

711
01:03:29,747 --> 01:03:34,616
I want to be certain that he knows
how great is my love for everyone.

712
01:03:34,667 --> 01:03:37,306
And this love belongs to him!

713
01:03:37,347 --> 01:03:41,659
I'm sure that, if he could
see his mother...

714
01:03:41,707 --> 01:03:44,505
It might be a tender illusion,...

715
01:03:44,547 --> 01:03:48,699
..but trying to strive,
to see this... How should I call it ?

716
01:03:48,747 --> 01:03:52,626
This heaven on earth more
concretely, I assure you that...

717
01:03:52,667 --> 01:03:59,220
No, Andrea. I would like to have
a faith, an impregnable faith.

718
01:03:59,267 --> 01:04:03,658
In this heaven on earth
there would be no place for Michel,...

719
01:04:03,707 --> 01:04:06,426
..for he isn't alive anymore.

720
01:04:06,467 --> 01:04:13,179
The paradise I dream about it's not just
for the living, but for everyone.

721
01:04:13,227 --> 01:04:18,142
It's eternal.
This is my paradise.

722
01:07:35,507 --> 01:07:38,499
Dera, don't let her run !

723
01:07:38,547 --> 01:07:42,460
Stop it,
you idiot ! Shut up!

724
01:07:43,907 --> 01:07:47,980
- What are you doing here ?
- Nothing, just passing.

725
01:07:48,027 --> 01:07:50,780
They drove me crazy !

726
01:07:50,827 --> 01:07:54,263
I'm feverish and can't stand on my feet !
I'm extremely cold !

727
01:07:54,307 --> 01:07:56,457
Why don't you go home ?

728
01:07:56,507 --> 01:08:01,501
I can't afford the night bus,
I have to wait for the tram.

729
01:08:01,547 --> 01:08:05,222
- Don't worry, I'll escort you.
- Are you showing compassion ?

730
01:08:05,267 --> 01:08:09,499
No, I'm going to the
neighborhood as well. Come.

731
01:08:14,947 --> 01:08:18,576
- Bye, beauty ! Have a good trip !
-Go fuck yourself !

732
01:08:18,627 --> 01:08:23,018
Farewell, goldilocks!
Say hello to Primavalle !

733
01:08:35,867 --> 01:08:39,416
I feel so sick ! What do you
come here for ?

734
01:08:39,467 --> 01:08:43,779
- I have to see someone.
- Who ? And at such an hour ?

735
01:08:45,547 --> 01:08:50,143
I don't know why, everybody
lies to me.

736
01:09:29,827 --> 01:09:35,857
Where's the key ?

737
01:10:02,947 --> 01:10:06,337
Where can I find a doctor ?

738
01:10:06,387 --> 01:10:10,300
How should I know ?
Go outside, ask someone.

739
01:10:10,347 --> 01:10:13,066
How could I tell you
where a doctor is to be found ?

740
01:10:47,347 --> 01:10:49,099
Where can I find a doctor ?

741
01:10:49,147 --> 01:10:52,378
I don't know. There's a chemist shop,
not that far from here.

742
01:10:52,427 --> 01:10:54,941
- Where is it ?
- This way.

743
01:10:57,267 --> 01:11:00,020
This lady needs a doctor

744
01:11:00,067 --> 01:11:03,025
Yes, it's for a very sick woman.

745
01:11:03,067 --> 01:11:07,618
Right now ? It's very late.
Anyway, let's try making a call.

746
01:11:14,787 --> 01:11:17,824
It's near enough. Thanks.

747
01:11:21,587 --> 01:11:24,306
- I don't want to go to the hospital.
- No, no...

748
01:11:24,347 --> 01:11:28,386
- I want to stay at my place.
- Yes, your place, no hospital.

749
01:11:28,987 --> 01:11:31,626
Do not breathe.

750
01:11:35,107 --> 01:11:38,656
- I don't want to go to the hospital.
- OK.

751
01:11:38,707 --> 01:11:41,460
I want to stay at my place..

752
01:11:43,867 --> 01:11:48,497
- So ? - She's "gone". I'd send
her straight to the hospital.

753
01:11:48,547 --> 01:11:53,575
No, doctor, why give her this pain?
Isn't there any hope ?

754
01:11:53,627 --> 01:11:58,576
<i>What do you want ? Two, three, four
days, a week... And then, amen.</i>

755
01:11:58,627 --> 01:12:01,095
- Is there nothing we can do ?
- Nothing.

756
01:12:01,147 --> 01:12:03,536
Two years ago one could have,
cured her, maybe.

757
01:12:03,587 --> 01:12:06,897
But the sickness is in its last
stages... It took both lungs.

758
01:12:06,947 --> 01:12:09,905
Unfortunately we can just
wait for the end.

759
01:12:09,947 --> 01:12:12,415
Goodbye. Thank you.

760
01:12:28,727 --> 01:12:32,163
Oh, my God,
I feel so weak...

761
01:12:32,207 --> 01:12:36,485
My God, I feel so weak...

762
01:12:36,527 --> 01:12:41,840
- Yes ? - Open the window,
call Alfonso, he's in the bar.

763
01:12:41,887 --> 01:12:47,405
Tell him two bring two eggs
and a cappuccino. They're nutritious.

764
01:12:47,847 --> 01:12:50,645
- And a fried pastry.
- Yes, immediately.

765
01:12:50,687 --> 01:12:54,885
No, from the window.
- It'll be faster this way.

766
01:13:01,207 --> 01:13:03,277
- Good morning !
- Good morning !

767
01:13:03,327 --> 01:13:06,524
- Did you go to our place ?
- No, to Ines's, she's very sick.

768
01:13:06,567 --> 01:13:11,721
- She's just a comedian !
- This time she's very sick.

769
01:13:11,767 --> 01:13:14,884
- Can I help you ?
- No, thanks, I was going to the bar.

770
01:13:14,927 --> 01:13:17,361
- He will go !
- Ah, well.

771
01:13:17,407 --> 01:13:22,117
Bring her two eggs shaken in milk
and coffee and a fried pastry.

772
01:13:22,167 --> 01:13:25,796
- Go! Run !
- Thanks! How is your wife doing ?

773
01:13:25,847 --> 01:13:30,204
- Always the same.
Goodbye, Mrs. - Goodbye.

774
01:13:35,967 --> 01:13:39,277
- He's coming. - Oh my God, the fox furs!
I can't see my fox furs !

775
01:13:39,327 --> 01:13:43,843
Look in the wardrobe for my fox furs.
They steal everything here.

776
01:13:43,887 --> 01:13:48,039
You mean these?

777
01:14:02,367 --> 01:14:04,835
- Hello beauty, how are you ?
- What a cold hand !

778
01:14:04,887 --> 01:14:07,799
This is warm !
Who is she ?

779
01:14:07,847 --> 01:14:10,839
- Go away, I'm sick !
- Goodbye.

780
01:14:10,887 --> 01:14:15,199
- How much do I owe you ?
- Don't worry, nobody ever pays here.

781
01:14:23,447 --> 01:14:26,519
He's such a rude man...

782
01:14:33,847 --> 01:14:37,476
He's at it again!
He's driving me crazy ! Stop !

783
01:14:37,527 --> 01:14:41,440
- I'll go there.
- Yes, please, he's driving me crazy !

784
01:14:43,887 --> 01:14:46,481
Good evening, how are you ?
Still feverish ?

785
01:14:46,527 --> 01:14:49,963
No, luckily. Anything new ?

786
01:14:51,047 --> 01:14:54,119
Nothing. We found no traces.

787
01:14:54,167 --> 01:14:57,716
- And what about Andrea ?
- Nothing.

788
01:14:57,767 --> 01:15:00,600
He was followed, all his moves
were controlled.

789
01:15:00,647 --> 01:15:03,605
That investigator did everything
he could, to no avail.

790
01:15:03,647 --> 01:15:08,118
My God, I'm so worried !
Irene was completely bewildered !

791
01:15:08,167 --> 01:15:12,319
I imagined the most terrible things.
Ten days went by.

792
01:15:12,367 --> 01:15:16,599
Don't worry too much, I'm sure
we'll know something about it soon.

793
01:15:57,487 --> 01:15:59,762
Go, now.

794
01:16:16,647 --> 01:16:20,799
- It's so late. Go, if you must.
- No, I don't care.

795
01:16:22,087 --> 01:16:26,399
Maybe I'm gonna heat the soup
and come back soon.

796
01:16:42,167 --> 01:16:47,605
Heavy robbery in Trastevere !
One dead and one wounded !

797
01:16:47,647 --> 01:16:51,526
Bandits ran away on a grey car !

798
01:16:51,567 --> 01:16:53,797
Heavy robbery in Trastevere !

799
01:18:28,927 --> 01:18:31,077
Open, come on.

800
01:18:34,807 --> 01:18:38,516
Lady, Ines is dead.

801
01:18:38,567 --> 01:18:42,162
- Come on !
- What's going on ?

802
01:18:42,207 --> 01:18:45,085
- Tell her, if you're brave enough !
- Stop it !

803
01:18:45,127 --> 01:18:49,962
He's a killer !
Our son is a killer !

804
01:18:50,007 --> 01:18:52,475
His friends ruined him !

805
01:18:52,527 --> 01:18:56,361
They wanted to rob a bank !
They harmed a man ! One died !

806
01:18:56,407 --> 01:18:59,479
Shut up, all of you !

807
01:18:59,527 --> 01:19:04,476
- Why do you act like this with your parents?
- You, shut up !

808
01:19:04,527 --> 01:19:07,917
They are your parents !

809
01:19:07,967 --> 01:19:11,198
- Where's Remo ?
- He's calling the police !

810
01:19:11,247 --> 01:19:16,002
Damn! I can't take it anymore !
Be careful or I'll kill you !

811
01:19:16,047 --> 01:19:20,643
Don't move ! Stop it !
Run away ! Run !

812
01:19:20,687 --> 01:19:23,838
Give me the gun! Think about what
you're doing! Let them arrest you !

813
01:19:23,887 --> 01:19:28,165
Your conscience will ease !
You'll go, I'm sure ! Quick !

814
01:19:28,207 --> 01:19:32,120
It's the only way you have to save
yourself! Try to understand!

815
01:19:45,567 --> 01:19:50,083
- There. - Did the car go to get
the doctor? - Half an hour ago.

816
01:19:57,727 --> 01:20:02,198
The doctor is already here. Come on,
lady, quick, he wants to see you.

817
01:20:03,407 --> 01:20:08,003
So, you admit you helped
Puglisi Ferdinando to escape,...

818
01:20:08,047 --> 01:20:10,515
..when you heard that police...

819
01:20:10,567 --> 01:20:12,762
Yes.

820
01:20:12,807 --> 01:20:15,799
Then all I have to do is sending
your file to judgemental autohority...

821
01:20:15,847 --> 01:20:18,520
..and send you to''Le Mantellate''.

822
01:20:18,567 --> 01:20:22,845
- What's ''Le Mantellate'' ?
- The female prison !

823
01:20:25,367 --> 01:20:28,962
Can you tell why
you helped him escape?

824
01:20:29,007 --> 01:20:31,919
- Sure.
- Then tell me !

825
01:20:33,207 --> 01:20:38,201
He was so terrified, he might
have been capable of anything...

826
01:20:38,247 --> 01:20:41,478
..to kill, or be killed...

827
01:20:41,527 --> 01:20:45,042
- So you helped him escape.
- Yes.

828
01:20:45,087 --> 01:20:48,045
It's a crime.
Clear, isn't it?

829
01:20:48,087 --> 01:20:53,161
I'm sure the boy will come to be
arrested spontaneously..

830
01:20:53,207 --> 01:20:56,802
He's a poor man. He'll admit his crime.

831
01:20:58,007 --> 01:21:02,478
Tell me: if you are
what you say you are...

832
01:21:02,527 --> 01:21:05,644
Careful, as we're going to
investigate further, you know?

833
01:21:05,687 --> 01:21:07,882
Why did you leave your husband ?

834
01:21:07,927 --> 01:21:10,282
Why did you go to live
with a woman...

835
01:21:10,327 --> 01:21:14,286
How do you say? A bad woman ?

836
01:21:14,327 --> 01:21:16,921
Even she was a poor creature.

837
01:21:16,967 --> 01:21:19,879
Yes, sure, but explain it better, please.

838
01:21:19,927 --> 01:21:23,681
It's a long story.

839
01:21:25,167 --> 01:21:28,364
And maybe I don't even know it.

840
01:21:28,407 --> 01:21:32,366
Maybe I might
explain you why.

841
01:21:32,407 --> 01:21:38,846
Yes? It's me, speaking.

842
01:21:38,887 --> 01:21:43,722
Ah, well ! can you send him here ?
Did you interrogate him yet ?

843
01:21:43,767 --> 01:21:46,201
Good, thank you.

844
01:21:48,247 --> 01:21:53,321
So, Puglisi went in
at the central.

845
01:22:10,576 --> 01:22:15,691
<i>A mysterious woman
helps robber escape</i>

846
01:22:18,647 --> 01:22:20,763
- Have a seat.
- Dear doctor !

847
01:22:20,807 --> 01:22:23,685
- Good morning, lawyer.
- Mister Gerard.

848
01:22:23,727 --> 01:22:25,922
- How do you do.
- Have a seat.

849
01:22:28,847 --> 01:22:32,840
- Did you have time to study her case ?
- Yes, sure.

850
01:22:32,887 --> 01:22:36,721
On the newspapers somebody insinuated that...

851
01:22:36,767 --> 01:22:42,125
..there was a relationship of sort
between the lady and the boy. What a shame.

852
01:22:42,167 --> 01:22:47,195
I guess that after the boy
spontaneously went to the police,...

853
01:22:47,247 --> 01:22:51,559
..all of this thing just lost
its monumentum.

854
01:22:51,607 --> 01:22:55,725
-Go on.
- But there's another aspect.

855
01:22:55,767 --> 01:22:59,521
The social position of the lady
and her family.

856
01:22:59,567 --> 01:23:04,561
As I told you earlier, after the
death of her child, the lady...

857
01:23:04,607 --> 01:23:10,637
How can I say ? She lost herself,
she did some strange things.

858
01:23:12,207 --> 01:23:16,120
Keep in mind Mister Gerard's
position in Rome.

859
01:23:16,807 --> 01:23:19,120
He's the representative of one of
the most famous american brands.

860
01:23:19,887 --> 01:23:23,960
Him, the lady's mother coming
from America, the family,...

861
01:23:24,007 --> 01:23:27,283
..they did everything they could
to help her...

862
01:23:27,327 --> 01:23:30,558
..up until she, of her
own volition,...

863
01:23:30,607 --> 01:23:33,360
..abandoned her husband.

864
01:23:33,407 --> 01:23:37,195
Is it true that since she went away,
you had no news form her...

865
01:23:37,247 --> 01:23:40,762
..up until today, when you read
about this on the newspaper ?

866
01:23:40,807 --> 01:23:46,916
- Yes, it's true. - Didn't you think
about the idea I told you earlier ?

867
01:23:46,967 --> 01:23:51,279
The hypotesis of putting the lady
in a psychiatric hospital...

868
01:23:51,327 --> 01:23:53,477
..for a period of observation ?

869
01:23:53,527 --> 01:23:56,280
Yes. I alerted the authorities
about that.

870
01:23:56,327 --> 01:24:02,641
I believe it all falls under
the realm of prevention, on your side...

871
01:24:02,687 --> 01:24:05,326
..and in the interest
of lady Gerard.

872
01:24:05,367 --> 01:24:12,955
Maybe then we'll have the chance
to ease this scandal a bit.

873
01:24:19,567 --> 01:24:24,482
Why should I get visited ?

874
01:24:24,527 --> 01:24:28,156
- because the doctor advised you to.
- But I'm fine !

875
01:24:28,207 --> 01:24:34,157
I know. Don't talk now, please,
try to stay calm.

876
01:24:53,227 --> 01:24:56,264
- Gerard.
- There, at the end of the road.

877
01:25:38,627 --> 01:25:41,300
Good morning. Have a seat.

878
01:25:50,187 --> 01:25:53,099
Come, lady. One moment, please.

879
01:25:59,267 --> 01:26:02,339
I'll soon be there,
don't worry.

880
01:26:07,627 --> 01:26:09,618
Come, lady, come.

881
01:26:11,827 --> 01:26:14,625
- And my husband ?
- He'll reach you in a while.

882
01:26:43,107 --> 01:26:45,302
Help yourself in, please.

883
01:26:47,087 --> 01:26:49,157
Please.

884
01:26:50,687 --> 01:26:53,963
- Is my husband not coming ?
- He'll come, don't worry.

885
01:26:54,007 --> 01:26:57,079
- Is this my room ?
- Yes.

886
01:27:30,927 --> 01:27:35,637
Lady, I brought you a room vest
and the toilet essentials.

887
01:27:35,687 --> 01:27:40,317
If you let me know what you need...
I'll do everything you need.

888
01:27:40,367 --> 01:27:45,760
Cesira, don't act like a child,
i'm perfectly fine.

889
01:27:45,807 --> 01:27:50,403
And I'm counting on you
for the house to run smoothly.

890
01:27:50,447 --> 01:27:55,805
Oh, lady, why is this happening !
You've always been a good woman !

891
01:27:55,847 --> 01:27:58,964
They didn't have to
close you in here !

892
01:27:59,007 --> 01:28:04,525
Cesira, don't cry.
See, I'm fine enough, here.

893
01:28:04,567 --> 01:28:08,276
Maybe it will be good for me
to be alone with myself, isolated.

894
01:28:08,327 --> 01:28:14,004
I'm calm here. Don't think
that somebody harmed me.

895
01:28:14,047 --> 01:28:18,120
Now that I'm not at home anymore, I'm
trusting you for everything to run smoothly...

896
01:28:18,167 --> 01:28:21,876
..and that Mr. Gerard might
have everything he needs.

897
01:28:21,927 --> 01:28:24,043
Cesira, may I trust you ?

898
01:28:24,087 --> 01:28:27,966
Yes, sure !
Oh, Lady !

899
01:30:09,687 --> 01:30:12,997
- Where are you taking me?
- The doctor wants to see you. Come.

900
01:30:16,927 --> 01:30:20,602
Everything is normal.
Try to flash it.

901
01:30:32,767 --> 01:30:34,678
Increase !

902
01:30:40,367 --> 01:30:42,562
Increase !

903
01:30:44,567 --> 01:30:46,956
Back to 4 !

904
01:30:49,487 --> 01:30:51,523
Stop.

905
01:30:51,567 --> 01:30:56,357
I'll show you some inkblot cards.

906
01:30:56,407 --> 01:31:00,685
Please tell me whatever comes through
your mind, when you see them.

907
01:31:00,727 --> 01:31:03,161
It's vital that you
collaborate actively...

908
01:31:03,207 --> 01:31:07,166
..and please try to give me
as many answers as you can.

909
01:31:07,207 --> 01:31:11,485
Also, do not omit anything
that comes through your mind.

910
01:31:20,407 --> 01:31:25,561
- But this... I don't know, it's nothing.
- What do you mean with "nothing", lady ?

911
01:31:25,607 --> 01:31:31,443
A fierce jumping beast.
A totem.

912
01:31:31,487 --> 01:31:35,844
- And then ?
- A vertebrae.

913
01:31:43,687 --> 01:31:46,838
A bat.
Yes, probably a bat.

914
01:31:51,367 --> 01:31:54,723
Nothing.

915
01:31:55,847 --> 01:31:58,645
Nothing. I don't know.

916
01:32:02,327 --> 01:32:07,606
They're just blots.
I don't know what to say.

917
01:32:07,647 --> 01:32:13,085
It's so ridiculous.
I don't know how to reply.

918
01:32:13,127 --> 01:32:16,483
Please, stop it,
it's really ridiculous.

919
01:32:17,287 --> 01:32:22,645
Something happened
to me and I can't solve it.

920
01:32:22,687 --> 01:32:27,841
I would like
a word of advice.

921
01:32:27,887 --> 01:32:31,004
- Good morning, reverend.
- Good morning.

922
01:32:31,047 --> 01:32:33,402
So if I...

923
01:32:33,447 --> 01:32:37,520
- But I must talk to the father !
- Stay calm.

924
01:32:37,567 --> 01:32:40,639
- It's important.
- We'll talk later. I'm staying.

925
01:32:42,247 --> 01:32:45,398
- Is that the new patient,
Mrs. Gerard ? - Yes.

926
01:32:45,447 --> 01:32:49,725
- May I speak to her ?
- Sure. Go on, please.

927
01:33:02,887 --> 01:33:04,957
- What do you want from me ?!
- What's up ?

928
01:33:05,007 --> 01:33:08,920
- I don't want anything to do with you!
Who are you?! - Don't you know me ?

929
01:33:19,567 --> 01:33:25,403
- Good morning. - Good morning.
- How are you ? - Fine, thanks.

930
01:33:25,447 --> 01:33:29,759
I would like to talk to you.
Nobody told me to do it.

931
01:33:31,587 --> 01:33:34,499
I met your husband.

932
01:33:35,267 --> 01:33:39,658
You know, he comes everyday
to have news about you.

933
01:33:39,707 --> 01:33:43,541
We spoke for long, it was
really enlightening.

934
01:33:43,587 --> 01:33:48,138
- So, I thought of visiting you.
- Yes...

935
01:33:48,187 --> 01:33:52,977
In our clerical practice we learn
to understand many things.

936
01:33:53,027 --> 01:33:57,703
Don't think I want to judge you
for leaving your home,...

937
01:33:57,747 --> 01:34:01,137
..or for being interested
in another man.

938
01:34:01,187 --> 01:34:03,906
No, you are wrong.

939
01:34:03,947 --> 01:34:08,179
I know my husband believed it,
but it isn't true.

940
01:34:08,227 --> 01:34:12,778
Let me explain:
there comes a time when...

941
01:34:12,827 --> 01:34:16,376
..love for our dearest ones
is not enough anymore.

942
01:34:16,427 --> 01:34:22,775
I felt it was too selfish,
shabby.

943
01:34:22,827 --> 01:34:26,217
And i felt compelled to get
close to the others,...

944
01:34:26,267 --> 01:34:28,827
..the humbles, any of the humbles,
and love them.

945
01:34:28,867 --> 01:34:33,304
This goes to prove yours is a christian feeling.

946
01:34:33,347 --> 01:34:37,659
Anyway, even love has rules that
need to be respected.

947
01:34:37,707 --> 01:34:40,665
Surely you ain't sure you need
to abandon your husband...

948
01:34:40,707 --> 01:34:43,016
..for the sake of a feeling,
as vast as it might be.

949
01:34:43,067 --> 01:34:47,060
We must do good, but carefully,
as God's will dictates.

950
01:34:47,107 --> 01:34:49,462
No, love has no measures.

951
01:34:49,507 --> 01:34:52,817
Evil sprouts from the fact that
we don't give all our love...

952
01:34:52,867 --> 01:34:55,825
..to those who mostly need it.

953
01:34:55,867 --> 01:35:00,702
We must love them for what they are
and help them the best we can.

954
01:35:00,747 --> 01:35:04,296
God created us as such.

955
01:35:04,347 --> 01:35:08,056
How sad it is to be suddenly aware
that in life...

956
01:35:08,107 --> 01:35:11,338
..we have been deserters towards
others and towards ourselves.

957
01:35:11,387 --> 01:35:15,380
So you would like to...
be a reformer.

958
01:35:15,427 --> 01:35:21,059
Did you think about it? Do you
you think you could have such a strength?

959
01:35:21,107 --> 01:35:23,177
I don't know.

960
01:35:23,227 --> 01:35:28,585
All I know is that I've been, and
still am, too selfish.

961
01:35:28,627 --> 01:35:33,382
I try to give others all the love
I have. Which isn't mine.

962
01:35:36,227 --> 01:35:42,382
Only then a great light
descends within me.

963
01:35:42,427 --> 01:35:48,821
An immense good possesses me
without me invoking it.

964
01:35:48,867 --> 01:35:54,066
Just then mountains could
really be moved.

965
01:35:54,107 --> 01:35:58,100
Do you firmly believe
in God and his own Grace ?

966
01:35:59,387 --> 01:36:03,426
What I know is that we need to
live full of love for everyone else.

967
01:36:03,467 --> 01:36:06,823
What matters is that men might
save themselves,...

968
01:36:06,867 --> 01:36:10,576
..that the whole world might.

969
01:36:11,227 --> 01:36:16,460
''I came not on earth to lose sinners,
but to save them''

970
01:36:16,507 --> 01:36:20,102
This is the miracle
of Christianity.

971
01:36:20,147 --> 01:36:26,700
Where did you read those things ?
Who told them to you ?

972
01:36:26,747 --> 01:36:30,740
- Nobody.
- These are words from the Gospels.

973
01:36:30,787 --> 01:36:35,417
I've been a sinner myself.
I... am in turmoil.

974
01:36:35,167 --> 01:36:37,886
Aren't you afraid of the
life you are choosing ?

975
01:36:37,627 --> 01:36:40,539
Why should I be afraid?

976
01:37:06,427 --> 01:37:09,180
- Ester ! Maria ! Help !
- What happened ?!

977
01:37:18,207 --> 01:37:20,357
Wait !

978
01:38:09,927 --> 01:38:17,003
You're not alone.
Stay calm. I'll be with you.

979
01:38:19,927 --> 01:38:24,921
I'm here with you.

980
01:38:32,207 --> 01:38:36,997
- May I ? Good morning, Lady.
- Good morning. - You may go.

981
01:38:37,047 --> 01:38:42,565
How are you ?
Do you feel fine here ?

982
01:38:44,527 --> 01:38:48,122
Is there something we might
do for you ?

983
01:38:50,487 --> 01:38:53,365
See, in here we like to...

984
01:38:53,407 --> 01:38:58,117
..establish calm and serene
relationships.

985
01:38:59,007 --> 01:39:01,965
I know what happened
earlier today.

986
01:39:02,007 --> 01:39:06,478
That poor woman attempted
suicide... An unfortunate thing.

987
01:39:06,527 --> 01:39:11,396
Despite the most severe precautions
it's hard to predict...

988
01:39:11,447 --> 01:39:15,963
..what lenghts might
an obsessed woman go.

989
01:39:16,007 --> 01:39:19,556
Anyway, I would like to thank you.
You're a very brave woman.

990
01:39:19,607 --> 01:39:22,519
No, I'm not brave at all.

991
01:39:22,567 --> 01:39:29,484
Tell me: how could you do it ?
Did you feel a strength within ?

992
01:39:29,527 --> 01:39:33,122
That mysterious strength that pushes us
towards the suffering ones...

993
01:39:33,167 --> 01:39:36,876
..with the most exact, lovely
and strong desire...

994
01:39:36,927 --> 01:39:40,363
..to help them,
free them, save them ?

995
01:39:40,407 --> 01:39:44,195
Do you feel such a strength ?

996
01:39:46,647 --> 01:39:53,325
No... no...
I don't know, I don't know...

997
01:39:55,167 --> 01:39:58,603
If my informations
are correct...

998
01:39:58,647 --> 01:40:04,244
That criminal, the one from the robbery...
I can't recall his name.

999
01:40:04,287 --> 01:40:09,441
He has been led by
the same strength...

1000
01:40:09,487 --> 01:40:15,517
..a strength common between
the greater souls.

1001
01:40:15,567 --> 01:40:19,480
Had I believed myself
to be a great soul,...

1002
01:40:19,527 --> 01:40:23,361
..I would have been crazy.

1003
01:40:23,407 --> 01:40:30,040
And so is love, love
towards others, true love.

1004
01:40:30,087 --> 01:40:34,603
- No, it's hate.
- Hate ?

1005
01:40:37,247 --> 01:40:43,277
Love towards others springs
from the hate I feel towards myself.

1006
01:40:43,327 --> 01:40:47,878
For everything that is and have been mine.

1007
01:40:47,927 --> 01:40:50,919
It isn't anything else.

1008
01:40:51,887 --> 01:40:56,403
- Good morning, judge.
- Good morning. Have a seat.

1009
01:40:56,447 --> 01:40:59,519
I have come to talk to you
about Mrs. Gerard case,...

1010
01:40:59,567 --> 01:41:02,798
..she has been interned in
a psychiatric clinic.

1011
01:41:02,847 --> 01:41:06,635
- How is she ?
- Well...

1012
01:41:06,687 --> 01:41:11,203
- I brought you her medical file,
so you'll see. - Well.

1013
01:41:12,567 --> 01:41:16,242
I think it's time
to take a decision.

1014
01:41:16,287 --> 01:41:21,315
I think we should see to
her definitive internment.

1015
01:41:21,367 --> 01:41:24,484
- Then, with time...
- In the meanwhile, please leave the files here.

1016
01:41:24,527 --> 01:41:28,486
Anyway, I'll need to meet her,
and her relatives...

1017
01:41:28,527 --> 01:41:33,317
..her doctor, whoever has been
around her since her child's death.

1018
01:41:33,367 --> 01:41:37,201
- Sure you should.
- We could meet all of them at the clinic.

1019
01:41:37,247 --> 01:41:41,843
It would be the best thing to do,
to avoid further annoyances.

1020
01:41:42,447 --> 01:41:45,484
When social and religious ideas
are discussed...

1021
01:41:45,527 --> 01:41:48,166
..it's difficult to give
absolute judgements.

1022
01:41:48,207 --> 01:41:52,678
Especially today... there's no truth anymore!
Everything is seduction and propaganda!

1023
01:41:52,727 --> 01:41:57,198
So, are we in front of a missionary
or of an exhalted person?

1024
01:41:57,247 --> 01:42:01,240
Had the lady followed,
even with a fanatical fervor,...

1025
01:42:01,287 --> 01:42:05,041
..a religious or
a political creed... but as such...

1026
01:42:05,087 --> 01:42:08,841
Should we opt for Mrs. Gerard
to be right,...

1027
01:42:08,887 --> 01:42:13,881
..we should then strip of our
professional clothes, and follow her.

1028
01:42:13,927 --> 01:42:17,078
Sure, but then maybe we
won't be brave enough.

1029
01:42:17,127 --> 01:42:20,961
How many men that society condemned
as rebels in their days...

1030
01:42:21,007 --> 01:42:24,283
and burnt at stakes were right ?

1031
01:42:24,327 --> 01:42:28,923
Sure, but our call is to
defend society as it is...

1032
01:42:28,967 --> 01:42:31,720
..with its laws,
within its actual asset.

1033
01:42:44,467 --> 01:42:47,618
Daniela !

1034
01:42:49,347 --> 01:42:53,101
- Good morning !
- How are you, Mrs. ? - Fine, thanks.

1035
01:42:53,147 --> 01:42:58,221
- Good morning, Mrs. !
- How are you ?

1036
01:43:10,547 --> 01:43:12,902
Take the child.

1037
01:43:19,107 --> 01:43:21,018
George...

1038
01:43:22,107 --> 01:43:24,701
Please, would you sit down ?

1039
01:43:26,867 --> 01:43:29,859
Good morning, Mrs. Please have a seat.

1040
01:43:33,827 --> 01:43:37,979
Mrs., we are here to look
after your interests...

1041
01:43:38,027 --> 01:43:43,021
..we are here to protect you.

1042
01:43:43,067 --> 01:43:47,822
You can speak freely,
don't be afraid.

1043
01:43:47,867 --> 01:43:52,019
- What do you want to know ?
- Are you a communist ? - No.

1044
01:43:52,067 --> 01:43:55,377
- Do you wish to be a nun?
- No.

1045
01:43:55,427 --> 01:43:58,146
So,
what are your ideals ?

1046
01:43:58,187 --> 01:44:02,863
- I know you worked in a factory.
- Yes.

1047
01:44:02,907 --> 01:44:06,741
So, tell me: what are
your feelings, your reactions?

1048
01:44:06,787 --> 01:44:10,177
Stop it...

1049
01:44:10,227 --> 01:44:13,902
Don't cry. It's important for
you to tell me everything.

1050
01:44:13,947 --> 01:44:18,737
Be exact, please. What are
your programs, your ideals ?

1051
01:44:18,787 --> 01:44:25,101
The ideals of those who need me
day after day.

1052
01:44:25,147 --> 01:44:29,618
Help me understand. What kind
of feelings move you?

1053
01:44:29,667 --> 01:44:32,420
If going back to your house,
to your husband...

1054
01:44:32,467 --> 01:44:36,062
No. What good would it be,
to be back home ?

1055
01:44:36,107 --> 01:44:38,621
It won't save nor me nor the others.

1056
01:44:38,667 --> 01:44:43,183
It would be really easy
to return, really easy...

1057
01:44:45,747 --> 01:44:50,696
But I'll be back being what
I was before all of this.

1058
01:44:55,867 --> 01:44:59,780
Instead, I want to share the joy
of the happy,...

1059
01:44:59,827 --> 01:45:04,503
..the pain of the suffering,...

1060
01:45:04,547 --> 01:45:07,903
..and the anguish of those who despair...

1061
01:45:07,947 --> 01:45:12,020
I'd rather lose myself with others,
then saving myself on my own.

1062
01:45:12,067 --> 01:45:15,855
Only the one who is completely free
might blend in with all the others.

1063
01:45:15,907 --> 01:45:22,460
Only the one who is bound to nothing
is bound to all human beings.

1064
01:45:22,507 --> 01:45:26,898
This is what I feel.
And now I've told you everything.

1065
01:45:28,387 --> 01:45:31,345
I have nothing to add.

1066
01:45:34,547 --> 01:45:36,981
I spoke freely.

1067
01:45:37,027 --> 01:45:41,942
And now, you'll freely do what you
believe you should, for your own good.

1068
01:45:46,067 --> 01:45:48,581
Please help me to my room.

1069
01:45:50,347 --> 01:45:53,578
- Irene ! - Here's the lady !
- What happened to her ?

1070
01:45:53,627 --> 01:45:56,699
Nothing. Don't worry.

1071
01:45:56,747 --> 01:45:59,819
- Go away, childrens.
- Lady, but...

1072
01:46:02,387 --> 01:46:06,778
- What happened ?
- Unluckily, it's like we thought.

1073
01:46:07,547 --> 01:46:09,583
I want to see my daughter !

1074
01:46:09,627 --> 01:46:11,697
Mrs. Hamilton wishes to see
her daughter.

1075
01:46:11,747 --> 01:46:15,376
The lady wishes to see
Mrs. Gerard. Please, lead her there.

1076
01:46:15,427 --> 01:46:17,736
Please, Mrs., come with me.

1077
01:46:19,107 --> 01:46:21,621
- Dear judge...
- Eh...

1078
01:46:31,387 --> 01:46:36,586
Irene, Irene...
It's all for your own good, believe me !

1079
01:46:36,627 --> 01:46:39,539
- We only care for your own good.
- Yes, I know, but stay calm.

1080
01:46:39,587 --> 01:46:46,265
- My heart is breaking !
Irene, dear daughter ! - Stay calm, mom.

1081
01:46:52,027 --> 01:46:54,495
Farewell, George.

1082
01:46:58,227 --> 01:47:00,582
Farewell, Irene.

1083
01:47:33,307 --> 01:47:36,663
- What did you do ?
- Will you leave her here ?

1084
01:47:36,707 --> 01:47:40,746
- What are you doing ?
- She is not crazy !

1085
01:47:40,787 --> 01:47:46,703
She's a saint !
A saint ! Lady ! Lady !

1086
01:47:46,747 --> 01:47:50,786
- It's an injustice !
- Poor dear !

1087
01:47:55,947 --> 01:47:59,417
She's a saint,
she's a saint !

